{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_0113peDBGmM42w2TfcMpYvXs","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** `Quarkus 3.30.5` -> `Jakarta EE 10 (WildFly 31.0.1.Final)`\n\n**Outcome:** **Success** - Application builds, deploys, and all 5 smoke tests pass.\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Quarkus BOM/plugins with Jakarta EE 10 API + maven-war-plugin\n- Dockerfile: Changed from mvn quarkus:run to WildFly standalone deployment\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/entity/Contact.java (moved from quarkus.tutorial)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/ejb/AbstractFacade.java (moved)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/ejb/ContactFacade.java (moved + refactored to @Stateless EJB)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/web/ContactController.java (moved)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/web/util/JsfUtil.java (moved)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/web/util/PaginationHelper.java (moved)\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml (moved from META-INF/resources/WEB-INF/)\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/faces-config.xml (moved)\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml (new CDI config)\n- src/main/webapp/index.xhtml (moved)\n- src/main/webapp/template.xhtml (moved)\n- src/main/webapp/contact/Create.xhtml (moved)\n- src/main/webapp/contact/Edit.xhtml (moved)\n- src/main/webapp/contact/List.xhtml (moved)\n- src/main/webapp/contact/View.xhtml (moved)\n- src/main/webapp/resources/css/jsfcrud.css (moved)\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml (new JPA config replacing application.properties)\n- smoke.py (new smoke tests)\n- CHANGELOG.md (migration documentation)\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/ (entire old package tree)\n- src/main/resources/application.properties (Quarkus-specific config)\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/ (Quarkus static resources convention)\n```\n\n### Key Migration Changes\n\n1. **Dependencies**: Replaced 8 Quarkus dependencies with single `jakarta.jakartaee-api:10.0.0` (provided scope - server supplies implementations)\n2. **Packaging**: Changed from Quarkus uber-jar to standard WAR\n3. **Package names**: `quarkus.tutorial.*` -> `jakarta.tutorial.*`\n4. **EJB pattern**: `ContactFacade` changed from `@ApplicationScoped @Transactional` (Quarkus CDI) to `@Stateless` (standard Jakarta EE EJB)\n5. **Persistence**: Replaced `application.properties` (Quarkus config) with standard `persistence.xml` using JTA datasource\n6. **Resource layout**: Moved from `META-INF/resources/` (Quarkus) to `src/main/webapp/` (standard WAR)\n7. **Runtime**: Replaced `mvn quarkus:run` with WildFly 31.0.1.Final application server\n8. **Context path**: Application serves at `/address-book/` (WAR name-based context)\n\n### Smoke Test Results\n\nAll 5 tests passed:\n- Index page loads (HTTP 200)\n- Contact list page loads (HTTP 200)\n- Contact create page loads with form fields (HTTP 200)\n- JSF form submission works without errors\n- All pages return valid HTML content"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":126,"cache_read_input_tokens":88053,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":126,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":955},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7644972d-de55-42ce-94f0-5092bba75a4d","uuid":"6364199b-3355-4218-be03-94dbe9173923"}
